评论者大多给予游戏正面评价，但对于本作是否好于前作《开启的封印》则观点不一。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的汇总得分上，本作的86%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wireless.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensunthelostage|title=''Golden Sun: The Lost Age'' (2003-GBA)|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2008-01-20|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714074745/http://wireless.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensunthelostage|archivedate=2011-07-14}}</ref>不如前作的91%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensun?q=Golden%20Sun|title=''Golden Sun'' (2001-GBA)|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2008-01-20|language=en|archive-date=2008-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209190929/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensun?q=Golden%20Sun|dead-url=no}}</ref>；同样[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的87%<ref name="gr">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/561356.asp|title=''Golden Sun: The Lost Age'' at GR|publisher=GameRankings|accessdate=2008-01-20|language=en|archive-date=2012-10-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVv3znt?url=http://www.gamerankings.com/gba/561356-golden-sun-the-lost-age/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>也略低于《开启的封印》的90%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/468548.asp?q=golden%20sun|title=''Golden Sun'' at GR|publisher=GameRankings|accessdate=2008-01-20|language=en|archive-date=2012-09-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ahb84hJX?url=http://www.gamerankings.com/gba/468548-golden-sun/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而与此不同，在IGN读者票选游戏前一百名中，本作的第78位领先于前作<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff|year=2006|url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/071-080.html|title=Readers' Picks Top 100 Games: 71-80|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2008-01-21|language=en|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVvaZ7y?url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/071-080.html|archive-date=2012-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。本作排在《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》举办的全任天堂主机最佳200游戏的第69名<ref name="NP Top 200">{{cite journal|author=Staff| title=NP Top 200|journal=Nintendo Power|volume=200|pages=58–66|language=en|date=2006-02}}</ref>。

IGN为该续作打了高分，并做出了“游戏虽有违一般游戏续作之惯例，却仍旧是一款游戏佳作”的评价<ref name="ign pg2" />。虽然游戏制作人员没有变化，但新加入的复杂迷宫却更受玩家的欢迎<ref name="ign pg2">{{cite web|author=Harris, Craig|date=2003-04-10|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/393/393159p2.html|title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age (page 2)|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2008-04-10|language=en|archive-date=2012-10-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVwZ63d?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/04/10/golden-sun-the-lost-age?page=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而游戏后来也成为了IGN2003年4月的“月度游戏”<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff|date=2003-05-02|url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/400/400522p1.html|title=GBA Game of the Month: April 2003|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2008-04-11|language=en|archive-date=2012-09-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AhbAMbYE?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/05/02/gba-game-of-the-month-april-2003|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[电子游戏月刊|电子游戏月刊]]》的巴蒂尔·贝滕豪森认为游戏在各个方面都没能超越前作（在视觉、音效和感官上都大致和前作相当），但他也并不否认“这也同时意味着游戏是角色扮演游戏中的佳品”<ref name="egm-review" />。其他评论亦称游戏的画质和音效更为完美<ref name="gamespot pg2">{{cite web|author=Torres, Ricardo|date=2003-04-15|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/goldensunthelostage/review.html?page=2|title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age (page 2)|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2008-05-01|language=en}}</ref>。

一些文章批评了本作仍未改掉的毛病，其中就如战斗系统。IGN和《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》都认为游戏的战斗系统不够“聪明”；当预先攻击的敌人提前被杀后，其他攻击该敌人的角色就会自动防御，而非攻击其他敌人<ref name="ign pg2" /><ref name="gamepro">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/28950/golden-sun-the-lost-age/|title=Review: Golden Sun: The Lost Age|publisher=GamePro|accessdate=2008-04-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501185614/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/28950/golden-sun-the-lost-age/|archivedate=2009-05-01|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。《GameNow》的伊桑·艾因霍恩认为战斗系统除了“必须的PRG要素”和图像外将一无是处<ref>{{cite journal|author=Einhorn, Ethan|title=Golden Sun The Lost Age: The GBA's best RPG franchise returns in fine form|journal=GameNOW|issue=19|volume=3|page=37|language=en|date=2003年5月}}</ref>。[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]认为Camelot需要为游戏加入更多的特色，同时也批评游戏过长的开篇对话会赶走前作的玩家，还会让新玩家把本就不熟悉的地点与人物搞混<ref name="gamespy rev">{{cite web|author=Padilla, Raymond|date=2004-04-26|url=http://archive.gamespy.com/reviews/april03/goldensun2gba/|title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age (GBA)|publisher=GameSpy|accessdate=2008-04-13|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080211094930/http://archive.gamespy.com/reviews/april03/goldensun2gba/|archivedate=2008-02-11}}</ref>。

《失落的时代》在日本首周卖出了9.6万份，是当时最畅销的游戏<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff|date=2002-07-12|url=http://www.gamepro.com/news.cfm?article_id=24989|title=Top 30 Japanese Video Games 06/30/02|publisher=Game Pro|accessdate=2008-04-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080612153001/http://www.gamepro.com/news.cfm?article_id=24989|archivedate=2008-06-12|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。截至2004年11月21日，游戏在日本和北美分别售出了24.9万份和43.7万份<ref name="sales">{{cite web|date=2004-11-21|archivedate=2004-12-09|accessdate=2008-04-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041209193033/http://www5e.biglobe.ne.jp/~hokora/gbarank.html|url=http://www5e.biglobe.ne.jp/~hokora/gbarank.html|title=Game Boy Advance Software Best Seller Ranking|publisher=biglobe.ne.jp|language=ja|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

